BootStrap: debootstrap
OSVersion: bionic
MirrorURL: http://nbi-yum.nbi.ac.uk/software/ubuntu/mirror/uk.archive.ubuntu.com/ubuntu/ 

%help
AGAT has the power to check, fix, pad missing information (features/attributes) of any kind of GTF and GFF to create complete, 
sorted and standardised gff3 format. Over the years it has been enriched by many many tools to perform just about any tasks that 
is possible related to GTF/GFF format files (sanitizing, conversions, merging, modifying, filtering, FASTA sequence extraction, 
adding information, etc). Comparing to other methods AGAT is robust to even the most despicable GTF/GFF files.

[Dainat J. AGAT: Another Gff Analysis Toolkit to handle annotations in any GTF/GFF format.  
(Version v0.9.2). Zenodo. https://www.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3552717]

%labels
maintainer Eugene Basson
ref RCSUPPORT-675
application Agat
applicationversion 0.9.2
institute JIC
install-version 1.0
provides agat_convert_bed2gff.pl, agat_sp_filter_feature_by_attribute_presence.pl, agat_sp_manage_UTRs.pl, agat_convert_embl2gff.pl, agat_sp_filter_feature_by_attribute_value.pl,
